      <title>特朗普的顾问希望将 SALT 冲销限额降至 10,000 美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/salt-tax-write-off-trump-advisers-want-to-cut-limit-to-below-10-000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为唐纳德·特朗普提供咨询的经济学家正在推动对州和地方税收减免设置上限，从而限制了纽约州、新泽西州和加利福尼亚州许多居民的宝贵税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/salt-tax-write-off-trump-advisers-want-to-cut-limit-to-below-10-000</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 20:29:41 GMT</pubDate>
